This Privacy Policy describes how the ScreenCat app handles your data.

### 1. Data We Collect
ScreenCat does **not** collect, transmit, or store any personal data on external servers.  
All your screenshots, albums, and settings remain **on your device only**.

### 2. Screenshots & Albums
Your images are stored locally in the app’s private container.  
We do not upload, share, analyze, or access your photos.

### 3. App Usage Data
We do not collect analytics or tracking data unless you explicitly enable an optional toggle (coming soon).

### 4. iCloud Sync (Future Feature)
If enabled in a future version, screenshots and album metadata may sync via iCloud.  
Apple’s security and encryption apply.

### 5. Contact
For questions or feedback:
email: screencatapp@gmail.com
